AI Study Companion with Class-Specific Knowledge

This is basically a mini retrieval-augmented chatbot so far

instructions
Set Hugging face access token in the .env if you are loading data. This is not required but will speed things up.

run commands
1. python tokenizer.py
2. python data.py
3. python train.py

when in the google cloud run
source ~/venv/bin/activate

run the training in the background while cd in the src folder
cd ~/CS-5822-ChatBot/src

outputs to a training log that can be viewed use training.log in the args
nohup python -u train.py --force --max_tokens 400_000_000 > ../training.log 2>&1 &